{{define "content"}}
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Hero Section with Jar Image -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <div class="mb-8 transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
            <img src="/static/img/gratitude-jar.jpg" alt="Gratitude Jar filled with colorful notes" class="mx-auto rounded-lg shadow-xl max-w-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 gradient-text animate-fade-in">
            Gratitude Jar
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 animate-slide-up">
            "Feeling gratitude and not expressing it is like wrapping a present and not giving it."
            <span class="block text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">- William Arthur Ward</span>
        </p>
        <a href="/gratitude" class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-orange-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full hover:from-orange-600 hover:to-orange-700 transition duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1">
            Start Your Journey
        </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Mountain Sign Section -->
    <div class="mb-16 transform hover:scale-102 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300 border-t-4 border-golden">
            <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
                <img src="/static/img/gratitude-sign.jpg" alt="Wooden Gratitude sign with mountains" class="w-full rounded-lg mb-8 transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700">
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-8">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-plum mb-4">What would happen if...</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        We made gratitude our highest priority, recognizing the beauty in each moment and intentionally sharing our appreciation with others?
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Pen and Writing Section -->
    <div class="mb-16 transform hover:scale-102 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300 border-t-4 border-raspberry">
            <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
                <img src="/static/img/gratitude-writing.jpg" alt="Pen and handwritten gratitude notes" class="w-full rounded-lg mb-8 transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700">
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-8">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-plum mb-4">Express Your Gratitude</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        Take a moment each day to write down what you're grateful for. Let your thoughts flow freely and capture the moments that make life beautiful.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- I Believe Section -->
    <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFB200] to-[#EB5B00] text-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg transform hover:scale-102 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">I believe...</h2>
            <p class="text-white/90">
                As we acknowledge the way our lives are intertwined, the vibrational foundations of our relationships 
                will begin to shift. We will begin to feel more connected, less separate from one another, 
                and our relationships and connections will become stronger.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#D91656] to-[#640D5F] text-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg transform hover:scale-102 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">I believe...</h2>
            <p class="text-white/90">
                As our dominant feelings became ones of appreciation, we will become more and more courageous 
                in sharing our gratitude with others. Gratitude will spread.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#EB5B00] to-[#D91656] text-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg transform hover:scale-102 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">I believe...</h2>
            <p class="text-white/90">
                As our individual characters continue to deepen, so too will our happiness and the happiness 
                of those around us. The world will become a more peaceful and loving place, driven by the 
                simple act of cultivating and expressing appreciation to one another.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    :root {
        --color-golden: #FFB200;
        --color-orange: #EB5B00;
        --color-raspberry: #D91656;
        --color-plum: #640D5F;
    }
    
    .text-plum {
        color: var(--color-plum);
    }
    
    .border-golden {
        border-color: var(--color-golden);
    }
    
    .border-raspberry {
        border-color: var(--color-raspberry);
    }
    
    .from-golden {
        --tw-gradient-from: var(--color-golden);
    }
    
    .from-orange {
        --tw-gradient-from: var(--color-orange);
    }
    
    .from-raspberry {
        --tw-gradient-from: var(--color-raspberry);
    }
    
    .to-orange {
        --tw-gradient-to: var(--color-orange);
    }
    
    .to-raspberry {
        --tw-gradient-to: var(--color-raspberry);
    }
    
    .to-plum {
        --tw-gradient-to: var(--color-plum);
    }

    @keyframes fade-in {
        from { opacity: 0; }
        to { opacity: 1; }
    }
    
    @keyframes slide-up {
        from { transform: translateY(20px); opacity: 0; }
        to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
    }
    
    .animate-fade-in {
        animation: fade-in 1s ease-out;
    }
    
    .animate-slide-up {
        animation: slide-up 1s ease-out;
    }
</style>
{{end}}